Package com.soa.message.header

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Header
    This interface represents a generic message header that can be composed of a name and a value or set of values.
    HeaderParser  
    HeaderPart
    This interface represents a single component of a message header.
    Headers
    This interface encapsulates the lookup and manipulation of a set of message headers.
    HeadersFactory
    Interface used to create a Headers instance.
    HeadersFactoryService
    Holds a HeadersFactory so that it can be published as an OSGi service.
    MutableHeader
